&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://prometheus.io"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Prometheus&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true">&lt;/i>&lt;/a> is an open-source monitoring and alerting toolkit designed for reliability and scalability. Initially developed at SoundCloud in 2012, it&amp;rsquo;s now a graduated project under the Cloud Native Computing Foundation (CNCF).&lt;/p>
